Description: "The 'MoorePackage' is an R package designed for performing advanced vector analysis and manipulation using the 'chRoma' package. It provides a set of custom functions that allow users to analyze, transform, and visualize numeric vectors, leveraging the power of 'chRoma' for precise and efficient calculations. With 'MoorePackage,' researchers and data analysts can streamline their vector analysis tasks, making it an indispensable tool for exploring and understanding numeric data structures.".
